data.description: This 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home offers comfortable living in a convenient location. With 1,414 square feet of space, this residence provides ample room for your family's needs.  Features: - 2-car garage for secure parking and additional storage. - A gas fireplace adds warmth and ambiance to the living area. - The kitchen comes equipped with essential appliances, providing convenience for meal preparation. - A new roof was installed in 2022, offering added peace of mind for the future. - Seller credit is available, making upgrades such as paint and carpet negotiable with a full-price offer.  This property is ready for your personal touch and customization to make it your own. If you're interested in seeing this home, don't hesitate to contact us at 404-721-4116 to schedule your showing today. Discover the potential of 138 Sunnymeade Dr. and envision it as your new home.
